WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.400 --> 00:00:04.566
Mom, Xu Mei was taken away by my dad

2
00:00:04.566 --> 00:00:05.866
I have to go see him.

3
00:00:05.966 --> 00:00:07.800
Can you go to prison?

4
00:00:08.266 --> 00:00:11.066
This day is an important place for the gods

5
00:00:11.066 --> 00:00:13.433
Only those with the city master's order can enter

6
00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:15.433
You break in like this

7
00:00:15.466 --> 00:00:17.000
Once you don't see Luo Pei

8
00:00:17.100 --> 00:00:19.133
No chance in the future

9
00:00:19.133 --> 00:00:21.033
So what do we do?

10
00:00:21.100 --> 00:00:23.666
My dad is now blatantly looking for a mistress

11
00:00:23.766 --> 00:00:25.700
You can't stand that tone.

12
00:00:25.700 --> 00:00:28.400
Well, for a woman

13
00:00:28.400 --> 00:00:30.000
It's a disgrace

14
00:00:30.266 --> 00:00:31.800
How could I possibly tolerate

15
00:00:32.266 --> 00:00:32.766
Your dad's

16
00:00:32.766 --> 00:00:35.700
The main force of the city has been kept in the safe in the study

17
00:00:35.700 --> 00:00:38.233
The password he never told anyone

18
00:00:38.466 --> 00:00:39.966
So what do we do?

19
00:00:39.966 --> 00:00:41.400
It's very simple.

20
00:00:41.400 --> 00:00:43.133
He thinks he's perfect

21
00:00:43.133 --> 00:00:45.300
I already knew the password

22
00:00:53.266 --> 00:00:54.700
Sister Xu Mei

23
00:00:54.700 --> 00:00:55.300
Are you OK?

24
00:00:55.300 --> 00:00:57.166
Xu Meikun

25
00:00:59.066 --> 00:01:00.866
Xu Mei, please rest assured.

26
00:01:00.866 --> 00:01:02.500
I will definitely rescue you

27
00:01:02.500 --> 00:01:04.033
Useless Kun

28
00:01:04.266 --> 00:01:05.766
I'm allowed to confuse your dad

29
00:01:05.766 --> 00:01:07.866
He also wants my position as the head of the Luo family

30
00:01:07.866 --> 00:01:09.500
They won't let me go

